Poznám ťa celkom dobre.

24
00:02:29,056 --> 00:02:31,426
Niekedy si nerozvážny.

25
00:02:31,626 --> 00:02:33,585
Pusti ho!

26
00:02:33,586 --> 00:02:35,095
