32
00:02:59,946 --> 00:03:01,255
<i>Pán Jang.</i>

33
00:03:01,256 --> 00:03:04,656
<i>Ani si nedokážem predstaviť,
aké ťažké to pre teba bolo.</i>

34
00:03:05,286 --> 00:03:08,056
<i>Ale ži.</i>

35
00:03:08,626 --> 00:03:10,426
<i>Buď sám sebou, Sung Joon.</i>

36
00:03:11,166 --> 00:03:14,536
