Prečo to tak komplikuješ?

37
00:03:14,796 --> 00:03:16,196
Proste ži.

38
00:03:16,766 --> 00:03:19,666
<i>Ži, nech sa deje čokoľvek.</i>

39
00:03:20,206 --> 00:03:21,406
<i>Jasné?</i>

40
00:03:39,756 --> 00:03:44,326
