278
00:22:15,876 --> 00:22:18,206
<i>Prepáč mi, že som nebola pri tebe.</i>

279
00:22:20,506 --> 00:22:22,146
Prepáč mi to, Sung Hoon.

280
00:22:42,766 --> 00:22:44,266
Prepáč mi, Sung Hoon,

281
00:22:45,936 --> 00:22:47,706
