425
00:35:06,723 --> 00:35:10,062
Trefa. Ja som ju vzal.

426
00:35:10,063 --> 00:35:12,102
A ja som si ju vpichol do tela.

427
00:35:12,103 --> 00:35:14,703
Lee Sung Joona ste vzali omylom.

428
00:35:16,073 --> 00:35:18,302
Prečo by som ti mal veriť?

429
00:35:18,303 --> 00:35:22,213
Ako by taký hlupák odhalil
tvoj plán a ukradol kostnú dreň?

430
00:35:22,943 --> 00:35:25,013
Tak ako si ho odhalil?

431
00:35:26,013 --> 00:35:29,113
Viem to vďaka tvojim
krásnym rodinným vzťahom.

432
00:35:30,113 --> 00:35:33,183
